import React from 'react'; import { BarChart3, TrendingUp, Award, CheckCircle, AlertCircle, XCircle } from 'lucide-react'; const ScoreSummary = ({ scores }) => { const goodScores = scores.filter(s => s.score === 'good').length; const averageScores = scores.filter(s => s.score === 'average').length; const badScores = scores.filter(s => s.score === 'bad').length; const totalScores = scores.length; const goodPercentage = totalScores > 0 ? Math.round((goodScores / totalScores) * 100) : 0; const averagePercentage = totalScores > 0 ? Math.round((averageScores / totalScores) * 100) : 0; const badPercentage = totalScores > 0 ? Math.round((badScores / totalScores) * 100) : 0; const highestScoringFont = scores .filter(s => s.score === 'good') .sort((a, b) => b.font.score - a.font.score)[0]; return (
{/* Header */}

Scoring Summary

{totalScores} scored
{/* Score Distribution */}

Score Distribution

{/* Good Scores */}
Good Matches
{goodScores}
{goodPercentage}%
{/* Average Scores */}
Average Matches
{averageScores}
{averagePercentage}%
{/* Bad Scores */}
Bad Matches
{badScores}
{badPercentage}%
{/* Highest Scoring Font */}

Top Performance

{highestScoringFont ? (
Highest Rated Font

{highestScoringFont.font.family_name}

{highestScoringFont.font.style_name}

Score
{highestScoringFont.font.score.toFixed(1)}
Foundry: {highestScoringFont.font.foundry_name}
) : (

No good matches yet

Score some fonts to see top performers

)}
{/* Progress Bar */} {totalScores > 0 && (
Overall Success Rate {goodPercentage}%
)} {/* Footer */}
Good: {goodScores}
Average: {averageScores}
Bad: {badScores}
); }; export default ScoreSummary;
